~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : write                                     ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : write [<message>]  or  write <boardname><enter>

   This writes a message on the board of the room you are in. If 
   you omit the test you are put into the line editor to enter your 
   message in that.  If you are a wiz you may write messages to the 
   wiznote.  If you are an admin you may write messages to the admnote
   and the news.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : read, wipe, search
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
